@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@adminToken = COLE_O_TOKEN_ADMIN_AQUI
@nfseId = 1

### 1. Consultar CNPJ e criar/atualizar cliente tomador
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cnpj/consultar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cnpj": "52643976000186",
  "email": "cliente@email.com",
  "whatsapp": "67999999999",
  "nome": "Cliente Teste"
}

### 2. Fluxo completo NFS-e mock
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/testes/nfse/fluxo-completo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cnpj": "52643976000186",
  "email": "cliente@email.com",
  "whatsapp": "67999999999",
  "planoId": "contabilidade_basico"
}

### 3. Listar NFS-e geradas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/nfse
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 4. Ver detalhe da emissao
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/nfse/{{nfseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 5. Baixar XML DPS
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/nfse/{{nfseId}}/xml-dps
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6. Baixar XML NFS-e se existir
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/nfse/{{nfseId}}/xml-nfse
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7. Enviar ou reenviar e-mail da nota se SMTP estiver configurado
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/nfse/{{nfseId}}/enviar-email
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 8. Tentar novamente se a emissao estiver com status erro
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/nfse/{{nfseId}}/tentar-novamente
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}
